value.name: The Righteous Brothers Live on the Sunset Strip
value.original_name: The Righteous Brothers Live on the Sunset Strip
value.overview: TV special from a live performance at the Roxy in L.A. in 1983 by Bill Medley and Bobby Hatfield. Singing all their top 10 hits  and Bill Medley's solo hit "Brown Eyed Woman".  They also sang covers of"Old Time Rock Roll", "Soul Man" and "Hold On I'm Coming"..
